{
  "texts": [
    "For a sequence of length T, it computes a matrix A 2 0; 1 T × T (attention matrix) with pairwise attention scores.",
    "The element A i;j determines how strongly the encoding of the token at position i should pay attention to the token at position j.",
    "The rows are normalised to have unit sum.",
    "The attention matrix A is calculated from the input sequence itself (hence the term self-attention).",
    "This basically gives weights according to the importance of certain words in the entire sentence."
  ]
}